@hostname = https://localhost:7058

### ============================================================================
### FHIR GraphQL ($graphql) — Multi-Tenant Examples
### ============================================================================
### These examples demonstrate tenant-scoped GraphQL queries.
### Single-tenant deployments can use /$graphql directly (see graphql-examples.http).
### ============================================================================

### 1.1 Get Admin Token (for authenticated endpoints)
# @name adminToken
POST {{hostname}}/connect/token
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

grant_type=client_credentials
&client_id=fhir-admin-client
&client_secret=dev-secret
&scope=system/*.cruds

### ============================================================================
### TENANT-EXPLICIT QUERIES
### ============================================================================

### 2.1 Tenant list search
POST {{hostname}}/tenant/1/$graphql
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "{ PatientList(_count: 5) { id name { family } } }"
}

### 2.2 Tenant instance query
POST {{hostname}}/tenant/1/Patient/example/$graphql
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "{ id name { family given } birthDate }"
}

### 2.3 Tenant connection search with pagination
POST {{hostname}}/tenant/1/$graphql
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "{ PatientConnection(_count: 5, _total: \"accurate\") { count pagesize offset edges { mode score resource { id name { family given } birthDate } } next previous } }"
}

### 2.4 Tenant multi-resource query
POST {{hostname}}/tenant/1/$graphql
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "{ patients: PatientList(_count: 3) { id name { text } } observations: ObservationList(category: \"vital-signs\", _count: 3) { id code { coding { display } } valueQuantity { value unit } } }"
}

### 2.5 Tenant instance query with reverse references
POST {{hostname}}/tenant/1/Patient/example/$graphql
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "{ id name { family given } ConditionList(_reference: \"patient\", _count: 10) { id code { coding { display } } clinicalStatus { coding { code } } } }"
}

